            <thetext>Steps to reproduce:

1) Open the Mobile Showcase in IE11 on a touch-capable device
2) In the Carousel demo, begin swiping a page, move your finger over the row of pagination buttons at the bottom of the screen and release.

Observed Result:
The Carousel page hangs in a half-opened position

Expected Result:
The Carousel page should be fully opened or closed depending on where exactly the swipe gesture ended.</thetext>
